0:00:34.195,000 --> 0:00:35,000
but it occurred to me

14
0:00:35.611,000 --> 0:00:36,000
that while the subject matter

15
0:00:37.322,000 --> 0:00:38,000
of the class is advanced

16
0:00:38.611,000 --> 0:00:38,000
and modern,

17
0:00:39.299,000 --> 0:00:41,000
the teaching technology isn't.

18
0:00:41.618,000 --> 0:00:43,000
In fact, I use basically

19
0:00:43.954,000 --> 0:00:45,000
the same technology as

20
0:00:46.324,000 --> 0:00:48,000
this 14th-century classroom.

21
0:00:48.954,000 --> 0:00:5,000
Note the textbook,

22
0:00:51.754,000 --> 0:00:53,000
the sage on the stage,

